nt||pn|Hand 31|
md|4hsak63hkt73dq983cj|
mb|1cxp1sp?|
pg| ***** 10 ***** |


nt|
^*bHand 31^*n @2is a minimum take out double with four spades. Show this by bidding 2@s. This promises no extra values, just four spades.
@4|
